Class AnimationModelImpl.Builder

java.lang.Object
cs3500.easyanimator.model.AnimationModelImpl.Builder

public static final class AnimationModelImpl.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
implements AnimationBuilder<IAnimationModel>
Represents the builder class for an IAnimationModelImpl. Helps to parse through a file and create a model based on the data.
